name: James B Allen Library - Financial Aid

name: Rutgers Law Library

name: Willard C. Eddy Hall, Storrs, CT 06269, USA

name: Charles Lewis Beach Hall, Storrs, CT 06269, USA

comment: Only use if you are a student or there for a game!!! This is a middle/high school!! So please, don't randomly walk into the school!!

name: Copia
directions: In the back on the right

name: Liz's Market
directions: Near elevator. Go through dining area. Labeled as Toilet and Restroom 3322.

name: 5900 Messer Airport Hwy, Birmingham, AL 35212, USA

name: Brunswick Zone Circle Lanes

name: Flinders St station

name: The Coffee House (CoHo)
directions: This is their default restroom, no special instructions

name: Walmart Supercenter, Myrick Street, Ellsworth, Maine, USA

comment: Family bathroom that’s usually empty, don’t have to be a paying customer.

name: Сладкарница Пчела
comment:
You have to ask for the key, but I don't think you have to be a customer to use this bathroom. 
За ключ трябва да попитате, но не мисля, че е нужно да сте клиенти, за да ползвате тоалетната.

name: Community Of Christ

name: Corinne and Jack Sweet Branch, Salt Lake City Public Library
Central Perk
comment: You have to be a paying customer

Is very spacious, (four, maybe five times bigger than a gendered washroom stall.)

Says unisex toilets.
